trans-unit.source: In order to get the token just go here: https://www.geni.com/platform/developer/api_explorer and introduce it in the input file as GENIKEY. Notice that the key gets updated almost everyday... so everytime you are using this script you will need to do it.
trans-unit.target: In order to get the token just go here: https://www.geni.com/platform/developer/api_explorer and introduce it in the input file as GENIKEY. Notice that the key gets updated almost everyday... so everytime you are using this script you will need to do it.

trans-unit.source: In order to use the interface, you will need to generate an application card inside Geni and obtain a key. You can create the application card in this: location https://www.geni.com/platform/developer/api_explorer, the key will be only valid for 24h, so you will need to register again the key regularly.

trans-unit.source: The file GeniTools is the one I am using as main programme. It is not yet very stable, but the libraries are getting. Just use the input file "INPUT_TEMPLATE" and select as input inside the script GeniTools.py, the input file needs to include the Geni token and the starting profile.
trans-unit.target: Файл GeniTools-это тот,который я использую в качестве основной программы.Он еще не очень стабилен,но библиотеки становятся все более и более популярными.Просто используйте входной файл "INPUT_TEMPLATE" и выберите в качестве входного внутри скрипта GeniTools.py,во входной файл необходимо включить маркер Geni и стартовый профиль.
